All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActiveSurveyPage
    ActiveSurveyPage is shown when doing a survey and updates the butons corresponding to the current question of the given survey.
    AdminPanel
    AdminPanel is shown when an admin is logged in.
    DecryptPassword
    The class DecryptPassword, decrypts the already encrypted usernames and passwords.
    EncryptPassword
    EncryptPassword gets a string and converts it to hexadecimal representation.
    GetInfo
    GetInfo class with overloaded methods that gets different types of information depending on which version is called.
    HelpPage
    The class HelpPage shows the the help "answers" via the Jpanel and contains the HelpPage GUIForm generated code.
    LoginCheck
    LoginCheck matches the given username and password and return true only if they match what is in the database.
    LoginForm
    LoginForm handles actions on fields and buttons.
    Main
    the Main class starts the application by the main method, which opens a new MainFrame class.
    MainFrame
    The MainFrame class, sets the properties of the window that the application is running.
    MainScreen
    The class MainScreen contains buttons to let the user navigate the different menus or simply log out.
    NewSurveyForm
    The class NewSurveyForm will be where an admin can add a new survey to the list of available surveys.
    PointSystem
    PointSystem finds the given username in the database and add the given points to his or her point sum.
    QrPage
    The class QrPage shows the QR code that represents the selected reward.
    QuickChartResult
    The class QuickChartResult is where an admin can see a visual overview of answers for a specific question.
    RewardPage
    The class RewardPage shows the buttons that grants the user rewards in exchange for points earned.
    SignUpPage
    The class SignUpPage gives the user the option of creating a user by entering an unused aau e-mail, password, name and gender.
    SignUpWriter
    SignUpWriter gets all the information given by the user when signing up for an account and saves it to the database.
    SurveyDelete
    The class SurveyDelete allows admin to delete surveys from application
    SurveyPage
    The class SurveyPage shows the user which surveys are currently available to take.
    SurveyWriter
    The class SurveyWriter opens the database and writes the SurveyID(the survey) the user picked and writes the answers of the user.
    ViewResultsForm
    The class ViewResultsForm shows the admin which surveys are currently available to see information on.
    ViewResultsQuestions
    The class ViewResultsQuestions shows the admin which questions are currently available to see information on from selected survey.
